  "electroenergetics.ponder.accumulator.header": "用蓄电池储存能量",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.accumulator.text_1": "蓄电池可以储存电能",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.accumulator.text_2": "用 24V 的电压给它充电",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.accumulator.text_3": "只需将正极与正极相连，负极与负极与负极相连",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.accumulator.text_4": "蓄电池就可以开始充电",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.accumulator.text_5": "储存电能后，蓄电池可以为其他设备供电",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.accumulators_series.header": "串联蓄电池",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.accumulators_series.text_1": "将蓄电池串联起来会叠加蓄电池的电压",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.accumulators_series.text_2": "每个蓄电池的接线柱分别与上一个蓄电池和下一个蓄电池相连",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.accumulators_series.text_3": "这组蓄电池组串联了十个 24V 的蓄电池，需要用 240V 的电压为其充电",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.alternator.header": "建造发电机",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.alternator.text_1": "发电机能够将应力转化为电能",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.alternator.text_2": "在转子周围放置磁铁",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.alternator.text_3": "发电机将会开始产生电压。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.alternator.text_4": "184V",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.alternator.text_5": "使用变压器来调整电压。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.alternator.text_6": "您或许可以考虑使用稳压器来进一步调节电压。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.header": "直观理解电力",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_1": "想象一条首尾相连的线。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_10": "对于灯泡来说，点的运动会使灯丝升温至白炽化而发光。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_11": "另外，有多少点进入就有多少点出来。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_12": "这就是基尔霍夫电流定律。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_2": "在这条线上放置一些点，把它们看作是电。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_3": "就像链条一样，点可以运动，但无法彼此分离。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_4": "电压源会让链条动起来。它们从一侧推，并在另一侧拉。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_5": "要注意的是，点本身并不代表能量，点的移动才代表电能。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_6": "这实际上是一个短路。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_7": "这里没有电阻，电压源能够飞速地移动这些点！",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_8": "将一个设备接入到电路里。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.basics.text_9": "设备利用这些点的运动来获得能量。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.bulb_mob_spawning.header": "灯泡与怪物生成",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.bulb_mob_spawning.text_1": "灯泡会阻止怪物的生成",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.bulb_mob_spawning.text_2": "即使它并没有点亮",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors.header": "连接线缆",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors.text_1": "接线端子和线缆可用于传输电能。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors.text_2": "要移除已连接的线缆，可使用空线轴。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors.text_3": "绝缘电缆可以染色。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors.text_4": "命名牌可以为接线端子命名。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors.text_5": "当准星指向接线端子时，将会显示它的名称",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors_chunks.header": "在未加载的区块传输电力",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.connectors_chunks.text_1": "在已加载的区块范围之外，电力仍能正常传输。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.current_transformer.header": "使用电流互感器",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.current_transformer.text_1": "有些时候，测量电路的电流很难",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.current_transformer.text_10": "切勿使电流互感器处于开路状态！",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.current_transformer.text_11": "电流互感器试图将电流从上部镜像至下部，但它做不到，因为底部电路没有闭合！",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.current_transformer.text_12": "最终结果是几乎没有电流流动，而底部的电压则飙升到了极高的数值！",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.current_transformer.text_2": "此处无法接入电流表",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.current_transformer.text_3": "电流互感器可以“传递”电流",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.current_transformer.text_4": "将电流表连接到底部的接线端子",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.current_transformer.text_5": "将顶部串联在要测量的线缆中",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.current_transformer.text_6": "电流表会显示所测量的电流值。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.current_transformer.text_7": "电流从电流互感器的顶部流过……",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.current_transformer.text_8": "……将会在底部形成镜像效果",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.current_transformer.text_9": "100A",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.header": "控制电流的方向",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_1": "这是一个好东西",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_2": "如果二极管的正极与电源正极相连，它将允许电流通过……",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_3": "....负极与电源负极相连",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_4": "这被称为单向导电性",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_5": "否则，电流将无法通过二极管",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.diodes.text_6": "反接的二极管将无法导电",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.electric_train_sounds.header": "改变电气化列车的音效",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.electric_train_sounds.text_1": "电车在通电时会发出不一样的声音",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.electric_train_sounds.text_2": "加入某些方块可以改变声音的风格",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.energy_meter.header": "使用电能表",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.energy_meter.text_1": "电能表可以计量消耗的电能",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.energy_meter.text_2": "将电源正极连接到 “进线端子”",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.energy_meter.text_3": "将正极的 “负载端子”连接到用电器上",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.energy_meter.text_4": "最后，把回路接在 “零端子” 上",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.energy_meter.text_5": "电能表将开始计量流经它的电能",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.gauges.header": "电流表与电压表",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.gauges.text_1": "电流表与电压表可以测量电路的电流大小与电压大小",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.gauges.text_2": "电流表可以测量电流大小",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.gauges.text_3": "它需要串联在电路中",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.gauges.text_4": "这意味着它需要连接在电路中。注意看它是如何监测电流流动的。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.gauges.text_5": "0.3A",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.gauges.text_6": "电压表可以测量电压大小",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.gauges.text_7": "它需要并联在电路中",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.gauges.text_8": "这意味着它需要连接在两根线缆之间。注意看它是如何探测这两个点并测量出电压的。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.grounding.header": "大地也是导体",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.grounding.text_1": "大地亦可导电。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.hv_switch.header": "放置高压断路器",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.hv_switch.text_1": "高压断路器可以用来连接或断开高压电路",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.hv_switch.text_2": "要制作一个这样的装置，需要将一个连接器置于高压断路器的方向上",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.hv_switch.text_3": "在它们之间间隔一个方块的距离",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.hv_switch.text_4": "高压断路器可以手动操作……",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.hv_switch.text_5": "...也可以用红石控制",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.header": "电气化列车",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_1": "接触网支架会自动附着到旁边的柱状物",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_2": "接触网可以为列车供电",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_3": "电气化列车需要有一个受电弓来与接触网接触……",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_4": "以及一个电动机……",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_5": "要向接触网供电，需要将接触网与电源正极相连",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_6": "将电源负极与接地棒相连",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_7": "2500 V",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.railway_electrification.text_8": "受电弓可以被染色",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.relay.header": "使用继电器",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.relay.text_1": "继电器本质上就是开关，只不过它是靠微弱的电流来驱动的",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.relay.text_2": "将控制电路连接至“线圈”接线端子",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.relay.text_3": "将被控电路连接至其余接线端",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.relay.text_4": "用扳手右击继电器，使其切换至常闭（NC）状态",
