  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer.header": "改变电压",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer.text_1": "变压器可以改变电压。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer.text_2": "只需设置比例。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_core_multiblock.header": "变压器铁芯基础",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_core_multiblock.text_1": "变压器铁芯可按特定的匝数进行绕制。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_core_multiblock.text_2": "加装散热片或采用水冷，可提升变压器的额定功率。",
