  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_losses.text_3": "299.4V",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_losses.text_4": "10A",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_losses.text_5": "损失的电能与线缆的电阻值以及电流大小的平方成正比（W = RI²）。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_losses.text_6": "变压器可用于提高电压，从而降低电流。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_losses.text_7": "3.3A",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_losses.text_8": "对于长途输电线路，提高电压可大大减少电能损失。",
  "electroenergetics.ponder.transformer_turns.header": "变压器是如何工作的",
